<plot>Blind Fear tells the story of a young blind woman haunted by the ghost of her deceased husband. Debbie wakes up in a pool of her own blood, she's been unconscious and one of her wrists have been cut. What happened? Her fragmented memories flashback to the previous two nights piecing together a psychological tragedy of murder and betrayal.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074685</url></doc>
